---
import "/src/styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy – fungery</title>

    <!-- Lexend Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lexend:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Favicon für verschiedene Größen -->
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/fungery_favicon_16.png">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/fungery_favicon_32.png">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="48x48" href="/fungery_favicon_48.png">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="64x64" href="/fungery_favicon_64.png">


    <style>
      :root {
        --beige1: rgb(255, 244, 216);
        --beige2: rgb(244, 234, 207);
        --lila1: rgb(106, 99, 169);
        --lila2: rgb(89, 62, 142);
      }

      body {
        background-color: var(--lila1);
        color: var(--beige1);
        font-family: 'Lexend', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: left;
      }

      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      a {
        color: var(--beige1);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
      }

      a:hover {
        color: var(--beige2);
      }

      .mail-link {
        color: var(--beige1);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .mail-link:hover {
        color: var(--beige2);
      }

      .top-logo {
        position: fixed;
        top: 1rem;
        right: 1.5rem;
        width: 80px;
        height: auto;
        cursor: pointer;
        border: none;
        box-shadow: none;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 4rem auto;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      footer.footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 2rem 0;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

footer.footer a {
  color: var(--rosa1);
  text-decoration: none;
  margin: 0 0.3rem;
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

footer.footer a:hover {
  color: var(--beige2);
}

    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- Small logo top right linking back to start -->
    <a href="/#start">
      <img src="/images/logo2.png" alt="fungery small logo" class="top-logo" />
    </a>

    <main>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

      <p>This Privacy Policy informs you about the type, scope, and purpose of the collection and use of personal data on this website (<strong>fungery.com</strong>).</p>

      <h2>1. Responsible Entity</h2>
      <p>
        Chris Freudenberger<br />
        Dreihäusle 3<br />
        78112 St. Georgen im Schwarzwald<br />
        E-mail:
        <span id="mail-container"></span>
      </p>

      <script>
        const user = "mail";
        const domain = "fungery.com";
        document.getElementById("mail-container").innerHTML =
          `<a href="mailto:${user}@${domain}" class="mail-link">${user}@${domain}</a>`;
      </script>

      <h2>2. Collection and Storage of Personal Data</h2>
      <p>
        When you visit this website, no personal data is collected, stored, or analyzed.
        No cookies, tracking tools, or analytics services are used.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Server Log Files</h2>
      <p>
        The provider of this website automatically collects and stores information in server log files,
        which your browser automatically transmits. These include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Operating system used</li>
        <li>Referrer URL</li>
        <li>Hostname of the accessing computer</li>
        <li>Time of the server request</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These data cannot be assigned to specific persons and are not merged with other data sources.
        The information is used solely to ensure the smooth operation of the website.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Contact via E-Mail</h2>
      <p>
        If you contact us by e-mail, the information you provide will be stored for the purpose of processing your inquiry
        and in case of follow-up questions. This data will not be shared without your consent.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You have the right to request information about the personal data stored about you,
        their origin and recipients, and the purpose of data processing.
        You also have the right to request correction, blocking, or deletion of this data.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy to ensure compliance with current legal requirements
        or to reflect changes in our services.
      </p>

      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> October 2025</p>
      
      <footer class="footer">
  <a href="/#start">Home</a> |
  <a href="/imprint">Imprint</a>
</footer>

    </main>
  </body>
</html>
